' Actor -> Use Case Associations
' ------------------------------------------------------------


User --> TL01
User --> TL02
User --> TL03
User --> TL04
User --> TL05
User --> TL06
User --> TL07
User --> TL08
User --> TL09
User --> TL10
User --> TL11
User --> TL12
User --> TL13
User --> TL14
User --> TL15
User --> TL16
User --> TL17
User --> TL18
User --> TL19
User --> TL20
User --> TL21
User --> TL22
User --> HK01
User --> HK02
User --> HK03
User --> HK04
User --> HK05
User --> PLG01
User --> PLG05
User --> PLG06


' ------------------------------------------------------------
' Relationships
' ------------------------------------------------------------


HK02 ..> HK06 : <<include>>
HK03 ..> HK06 : <<include>>
HK04 ..> HK06 : <<include>>
HK05 ..> HK06 : <<include>>

PLG01 ..> PLG02 : <<include>>
PLG02 ..> PLG03 : <<include>>
PLG02 ..> PLG04 : <<include>>


@enduml
